@q ** (2) circle_primary --> GET_CIRCLE numeric_primary sphere_primary@>
@*1 \§circle primary> $\longrightarrow$ \.{GET\_CIRCLE}
\§numeric primary> \§sphere primary>. 

\LOG
\initials{LDF 2004.10.13.}
